This file contains some of my plans for enhancements to R.
Kurt Hornik <Kurt.Hornik@R-project.org>

* Improve Aspell LaTeX filtering using parseLatex::parseLatex().
  With D Murdoch.

* Improve namespace registration of native routines.
  With S Urbanek.

* Work on the following PRs:

  ** <https://bugs.r-project.org/show_bug.cgi?id=18655>
     Enhancements to `*wilcox` functions for large population sizes

  ** <https://bugs.r-project.org/show_bug.cgi?id=18607>
     wilcox.test w/ EXACT=TRUE should give more accurate
     warning or compute PValue w/ Ties

* Improve classical tests: e.g. t.test() should really show the point
  estimate of the parameter of interest for which it gives a confint.
